Package: biblioview
Title: A Shiny Web Portal and Abstract Enricher for Zotero Libraries
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Thomas", "Petzoldt", , "thomas.petzoldt@tu-dresden.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides automated pipelines to fetch Zotero group libraries, 
    generate APA citations, and harvest missing abstracts from 
    external metadata APIs (Crossref, OpenAlex, and Europe PMC).
